s: 102<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/8/02 1:09:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=172.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Which cloak to use</span><hr size=1> Yes, but it all depends what's in your waist slot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uabazagaroth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Abazagaroth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/8/02 1:34:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=172.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.humanevolution.f2s.com/images/webring.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Which cloak to use</span><hr size=1> I don't think its worth it at all. White Bear Pelt Cloak &gt; Ancient Seahorse<br><br> <p>C. David Kreger, dkreger@yahoo.com<br>Webmaster:<br><a href="http://www.humanevolution.f2s.com" target="_top">A Look at Modern Human Origins</a><br>Moderator:<br><a href="http://pub19.ezboard.com/balookatmodernhumanorigins" target="_top">Human Evolution Message Board</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugaladril1961.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Galadril1961</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 250<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/8/02 1:41:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=172.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Which cloak to use</span><hr size=1> I'm using Cloak of Truth 15ac, 10str, 5dex, 8wis, 5cha, +5% m